# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## Unreleased

- Document the `release` branch workflow and require merge requests to target `release`
- Add agent instructions to keep pull request titles and summaries current and update the changelog on every PR
- Adopt `uv` as the default contributor workflow and lock the local development environment
- Replace Black, isort, Flake8, and pyupgrade with Ruff for Python formatting and linting
- Add Makefile help output plus dedicated `lint` and `format` targets
- Update contributor and agent documentation for the new development workflow
- Update the honeypot field documentation for the `aria-hidden="true"` accessibility attribute

## [1.2.1] - 2026-02-05

- Add locale support
- Add support for Python 3.13 and 3.14
- Add support for Django 5.1 and 5.2
- Add support for Wagtail 7.0, 7.1 and 7.2
- Drop support for Python 3.9
- Drop support for Django 5.0
- Drop support for Wagtail 5.1 and 5.2
- Update development dependencies

## [1.2.0] - 2024-07-13

- Upgrade for Wagtail 6.1 & Django 5.0
- Upgrade for Wagtail 5.2+ & Django 4.2+
- Update pr-commit config
- Fix typo in docs

## [1.1.0] - 2023-02-12

- Drop older supported versions
- Add python 3.11
- Remove pre-commit in CI
- Improve developer docs and setup
- Add testing for postgres and mysql

## [1.0.0] - 2022-09-10

- [#15](https://github.com/nickmoreton/wagtail-honeypot/pull/15) Add Wagtail 3/4 support and improve developer documentation and tools

## [Yanked]

- [#14](https://github.com/nickmoreton/wagtail-honeypot/pull/14) Add Wagtail 3.0 support

## [0.2.0] - 2022-02-24

### Added

- Initial release
